(i) All German Offices were burnt or. demolished.

(ii) The W/T Station and mast were destroyed.

(iii) The German car and lorry garage was destroyed.

(vii) The ammunition store on Maaloy Island was demolished.

(viii) The German barracks and Head- quarters on Maaloy Island were burnt out by the initia) Naval bombardment.
